  <title translate="true">How to Copy a Category</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">How to Copy a Category</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:16px; line-height:1.00; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">You can “clone” one or several of the selected categories. While cloning, new categories are created that are completely identical to the ones being cloned: image settings, relations between categories, access control rule settings, settings of triggers and templates, are retained.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">So as to clone the category, through the menu go to the list of categories, mark the required category and press the button “</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">Clone</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">”.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px; line-height:1.00; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><image src="category_delete_en.png" scale="100.00%" padding="1 0 1 0" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
  </body>
